            <title>[PIG-213] Non-static Log objects in org.apache.pig.data.* classes are inefficient</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-213</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LogFactory.getLog called from the constructor of Tuple accounts for significant percentage of my job&apos;s running time. The proposed fix is to make the Log fields static (which is generally standard practice).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
